{
  "stem": "1511.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We find spoons, we find shoes. we found from all these people when they were in there, where they were tortured, where they were taken from there to the oven someplace.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was very scary and terrible to live, and they organized.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then the Bricha came, and they organized that they can take us to Italy, but we have to walk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So in this concentration camp was kitchens, so the very religious people came there, and they took over all the kitchens.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they wouldn't let us in, because we're not religious.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we had to make fire outside and cook for the kids anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They ask us-- so when we were going to climb on the-- on the-- on the heights, on the-- Mountains?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--on the mountains on the-- Italy, and my husband was one of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That- he helped to blankets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came from-- they gave us blankets for everybody who came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every night, the people were taking through the-- like from the camps to Italy, Milano.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from there, somehow to Israel, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were still sitting there, and we were ready already also to go, and my husband had a sister in here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And good enough, we wrote there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She received somehow the letters, and they made us papers to come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in the meantime, we wouldn't need it, because the Jewish Congress brought from the people whoever is a dressmaker, whoever is-- and they came the register, and they went out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They all went, and we were still there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were sitting in Austria, and Veksheit was our big place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then because my husband helped so much, we got rooms in Bindermichel.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
